summary: This is a calendar entry for a planning/coordination meeting with the Southern District of New York (SDNY) regarding the Epstein case, scheduled for July 1, 2019. It appears to be a personal calendar entry created in advance of the meeting.

events.title: Planning/Coordination Meeting with SDNY on Epstein Case
events.description: A scheduled meeting for planning and coordination with the Southern District of New York (SDNY) regarding the Epstein case.

keyFacts: A coordination meeting between parties involved in the Epstein case and the SDNY was scheduled for July 1, 2019.
The meeting was categorized as 'X-PERSONAL' and was planned in advance, with the calendar entry created on June 28, 2019.
The document is a calendar entry, indicating formal planning was underway in the SDNY's investigation or prosecution related to Jeffrey Epstein in mid-2019.
